        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 5.—Flash coloration, hands, and feet in Leucostethus bilsa sp. nov. (A–E) live adult female CJ 7765; (F–G) live adult male holotype CJ 8311. Note the mustard-yellow paracloacal marks on the dorsal thighs (A), and the mustard-yellow flash marks on axillae, groin, and hind limbs (B, C). Photos by Diego Acosta-López." ;
